  ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  3.0.8  (29 Aug 2003)
    * Surfaced the OnPaint event in TRzDBRadioGroup. This is useful when
      GroupStyle is set to gsCustom.
    * When a TRzDBRadioGroup is connected to a dataset that is not active, the
      radio-group disables itself.
